<div class="container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to DTC Dental, a trusted dental clinic located in Englewood, Colorado. Established in 2006, we are dedicated to providing comprehensive dental care for our patients. Our clinic is staffed with a team of highly qualified professionals, including five dentists, five dental technicians, four hygienists, and six office staff members.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Services</h3>
    <p>
        At DTC Dental, we offer a full range of dental services tailored to meet the needs of our patients. Our services include preventive care, restorative treatments, cosmetic dentistry, and more, ensuring that we can accommodate a variety of dental health needs.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Team</h3>
    <p>
        Our dedicated team works tirelessly to provide top-notch dental care in a comfortable and welcoming environment. With a patient base of 2,500 individuals from over 900 different households, we are proud to be a cornerstone of the community.
    </p>

    <h3>Internal Management System</h3>
    <p>
        We are currently in the process of developing an internal web application to enhance our operational efficiency. This application will allow DTC employees to schedule patient appointments, record patient visits, and manage patient records effectively. It will not be customer-facing, ensuring a focus on internal processes.
    </p>

    <h3>Owner</h3>
    <p>
        DTC Dental is owned by John Roberts, who has entrusted our team to build this innovative web application for the clinic.
    </p>
